p;企業情報&emsp;\n                </a>\n                <ul class=\"dropdown-menu pc-drop\" style=\"margin-left: -311%;\">\n                  <div class=\"d-flex\">\n                    <li class=\"pb-3\">\n                      <a class=\"dropdown-item pc-drop-item\" href=\"aboutus_branches_japan.html\">\n                        <p class=\"\">事業所<i class=\"ps-3 fa-solid fa-chevron-right\"></i></p>\n                        <img src=\"./assets/img/head-kokunai.png\" alt=\"\">\n                      </a>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"pb-3\">\n                      <a class=\"dropdown-item pc-drop-item\" href=\"aboutus_branches_world.html\">\n                        <p class=\"\">海外拠点<i class=\"ps-3 fa-solid fa-chevron-right\"></i></p>\n                        <img src=\"./assets/img/head-kaigai.png\" alt=\"\">\n                      </a>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"pb-3\">\n                      <a class=\"dropdown-item pc-drop-item\" href=\"aboutus_branches_groupinc.html\">\n                        <p class=\"\">グループ企業<i class=\"ps-2 fa-solid fa-chevron-right\"></i></p>\n                        <img src=\"./assets/img/head-groupink.png\" alt=\"\">\n                      </a>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"pb-3\">\n                      <a class=\"dropdown-item pc-drop-item\" href=\"aboutus_info.html\">\n                        <p class=\"\">会社概要<i class=\"ps-3 fa-solid fa-chevron-right\"></i></p>\n                        <img src=\"./assets/img/head-info.png\" alt=\"\">\n                      </a>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"pb-3\">\n                      <a class=\"dropdown-item pc-drop-item\" href=\"aboutus_greeting.html\">\n                        <p class=\"\">代表挨拶<i class=\"ps-3 fa-solid fa-chevron-right\"></i></i></p>\n                        <img src=\"./assets/img/head-syatyo.png\" alt=\"\">\n                      </a>\n                    </li>\n                  </div>\n                </ul>\n              </li>\n              <li class=\"nav-item\">\n                <a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"./products_industrial.html\">|&emsp;取扱品目&emsp;</a>\n              </li>\n              <li class=\"nav-item\">\n                <a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"./material.html\">|&emsp;資料と動画&emsp;</a>\n              </li>\n              <li class=\"nav-item\">\n                <a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"https://www.recruit.otani-shokai.com\">|&emsp;採用&emsp;</a>\n              </li>\n              <div class=\"gtranslate_wrapper\"></div>\n            </ul>\n            <button class=\"btn-menu-pc z-1\">\n              <a href=\"https://contact.otani-shokai.com/contact\"><p class=\"text-white fw-bold\">お問い合わせ</p></a>\n            </button>\n          </div>\n      </div>\n      </nav>\n    </header>\n    <main>\n      <div class=\"top-bar card bg-dark rounded-0\">\n        <!--\n        <img\n          class=\"card-img opacity-25\"\n          src=\"./assets/img/greeting/bar-greeting.png\"\n          alt=\"\"\n        />\n        -->\n        <img\n          class=\"card-img opacity-25\"\n          src=\"./assets/img/greeting/bar-greeting_new.png\"\n          alt=\"\"\n        />\n        <div class=\"card-img-overlay\">\n          <h1 class=\"card-text text-white\">代表挨拶</h1>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <span class=\"pc-space-s d-xl-block\"></span>\n      <div class=\"px-3\">\n        <h2 class=\"text-center my-5 fs-3\">代表取締役社長 メッセージ</h2>\n        <span class=\"pc-space-ss d-xl-block\"></span>\n        <div class=\"col-lg-8 mx-auto\">\n          <div class=\"d-flex flex-column flex-lg-row align-items-center\">\n            <!--\n            <img\n              src=\"./assets/img/greeting/president.png\"\n              class=\"\"\n              alt=\"大谷商会代表取締役社長アルバート・ヴェツラーの肖像\"\n            />\n            -->\n            <img\n              src=\"./assets/img/greeting/president_new.png\"\n              class=\"\"\n              alt=\"大谷商会代表取締役社長ロバート・ヴェツラーの肖像\"\n            />\n            <div class=\"p-5\">\n              <img class=\"\" src=\"./assets/img/greeting/lessismore.png\" alt=\"\" />\n            </div>\n            <!--\n            署名は消す？？？　書いていただく？？？\n            \n            <img\n              src=\"./assets/img/greeting/sign.png\"\n              class=\"col-lg-3 col-5\"\n              alt=\"大谷商会代表取締役社長アルバート・ヴェツラーの自筆署名\"\n            />\n            -->\n          </div>\n          <span class=\"pc-space-s d-xl-block\"></span>\n          <p>\n            大谷商会は、産業機械・食品・花卉を取り扱う商社です。優れた商品とスピーディなサービスの提供で、設立以来お客様から信頼を頂くべく努力を積み重ねて参りました。その結果、多くの皆様より多大なご支援を賜り健全な成長を遂げ今日に至っています。今後も企業と社会が直面している様々な課題に対し、努力とチャレンジ精神をもって挑みたいと思います。\n            さて、世界の多くの国々では技術の進歩と国際貿易によってこれまでにないほど物質的には裕福になっています。しかしながら同時に我々人間社会は限りある資源を無頓着に使うなどの結果、昨今の環境問題を引き起こしているというのも現状であります。これまでのように企業・社会とも単純な成長目標を追及するだけではなく、一時的にはマイナスを招くことになるかもしれませんが「環境破壊をしない」・「環境を守る」というキーワードにももっと重点を置かなくてはなりません。\n            私どもはこの「環境破壊をしない」・「環境を守る」というキーワードから新たな需要の創造が可能と捉えています。大谷商会は、社会情勢の変化を受け入れ　環境に配慮し　持続可能な経済成長に貢献すべく邁進してまいります。\n          </p>\n          <p class=\"text-end my-5\">\n            代表取締役社長<br />\n            大谷太郎\n          </p>\n          <span class=\"pc-space-s d-xl-block\"></span>\n          <p>\n            As a family-based trading company with activities in the field of\n            industrial products, food, and flowers, our primary concern is\n            providing superior products as well as speedy and reliable service\n            to our customers so as to become their preferred supplier. While we\n            are proud of having achieved substantial growth by following this\n            path, we also see, with apprehension and expectation, the challenges\n            ahead of us and our society. Technological progress and\n            international trade have brought unprecedented material wealth to\n            the world. At the same time, human activities have created an\n            environment that is increasingly becoming unstable. Our hybris and\n            indifference towards nature often becomes apparent in the way we\n            manage scarce resources and make purchase decisions at the consumer\n            level. A clear shift of priorities away from pure growth targets\n            towards targets centered around the word ‘sustainability’ will be,\n            in the years to come, the major challenge to companies and society\n            at large. This shift will create disruptions in some industries and\n            create new demand in others. Although being a small player, we want\n            to be actively involved in this process of transition and\n            rethinking, and contribute to environment-friendly and sustainable\n            growth.<br />\n              <!--\n            <span class=\"fw-bold\">\n              <p class=\"text-end my-5\">\n                Albert Wetzler<br />\n                President\n              </p>\n              -->\n              <p class=\"text-end my-5\">\n                Robert Wetzler<br />\n                President\n              </p>\n            \n            </span>\n          </p>\n        </div>\n        <span class=\"pc-space-s d-xl-block\"></span>\n      </div>\n    </main>\n    <footer class=\"bg-light py-5 position-relative\">\n      <div class=\"foot d-flex flex-wrap justify-content-center g-0\">\n        <div class=\"col-lg-1 my-4 me-5\">\n          <p class=\"fw-bold\">事業紹介</p>\n          <p><a href=\"./business_industrial.html\">産業設備</a></p>\n          <p><a href=\"./business_unipro.html\">ユニプロ</a></p>\n          <p><a href=\"./business_world.html\">海外製品</a></p>\n          <p><a href=\"./business_food.html\">食品</a></p>\n          <p><a href=\"./business_kaki.html\">花き</a></p>\n          <p><a href=\"./special_unipro.html\">ユニプロへの想い</a></p>\n          <p><a href=\"./special_world.html\">世界を結ぶ大谷商会</a></p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"col-lg-1 my-4 me-5\">\n        